&INFO
 Bulk Silicon.
 k-point calculation with 8 atoms (conventional cell)
 and a symmetrized and shifted 2x2x2 MP-mesh.
&END

&CPMD
  USE_CUFFT 
  FFT_N_STREAMS_PER_DEVICE
  2
  FFT_N_DEVICES_PER_TASK
  1
  USE_CUBLAS
  BLAS_N_STREAMS_PER_DEVICE
  2
  BLAS_N_DEVICES_PER_TASK
  1
  OPTIMIZE WAVEFUNCTION
  CONVERGENCE ORBITALS
   1.0e-7
  PRINT FORCES ON
  MAXSTEP
  10
&END


&DFT
  FUNCTIONAL LDA
&END

&SYSTEM
  SYMMETRY
  1
  SCALE
  CELL
  10.263102 1.0  1.0  0  0  0
  CUTOFF
  30.0
  KPOINTS MONKHORST-PACK SYMMETRIZED
   2 2 2 SHIFT=0.1 0.1 0.1
&END

&ATOMS
*SI_MT_LDA  KLEINMAN-BYLANDER 
   LMAX=P
   8
   0.50 1.00 0.50  
   1.00 0.50 0.50
   0.50 0.50 0.00
   1.00 1.00 0.00
   0.75 0.25 0.75
   0.25 0.25 0.25
   0.25 0.75 0.75
   0.75 0.75 0.25
&END

&BASIS
  PSEUDO AO 2
  0 1
&END


